  line
  line `(i) in relation to proceedings before a High Court, prescribed by rules made by the`
  line `High Court; and`
  line
  line `(ii) in other cases, prescribed by rules made under this Act;';`
  line
  line `(iii) clauses (y) and (z) shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(b) in section 44, the words "or the Tribunal" shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(c) in Chapter VIII, for the Chapter heading, the Chapter heading "APPEALS" shall be`
  line substituted;
  line
  line `(d) sections 54 and 55 shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(e) in section 56,---`
  line
  line `(i) for the word "Tribunal", wherever it occurs, the words "High Court" shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(ii) sub-section (3) shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(f) in section 57,---`
  line
  line `(i) for the word "Tribunal", wherever it occurs, the words "High Court" shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(ii) sub-section (5) shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(g) sections 58 and 59 shall be omitted;`
  line
